Package interfaces

package interfaces
The interfaces package contains a collection of interfaces defining contracts for various functionalities. These interfaces provide a blueprint for classes to implement, facilitating consistency and interoperability across different implementations.
  • Interfaces
    Class
    Description
    IAdminService
    The IAdminService interface provides methods to manage/view staff members, branches, and payment methods.
    IAuthorisationService
    The IAuthorisationService interface provides methods for user authentication and authorization.
    IBranchListView
    The IBranchListView interface provides methods to display branch details.
    IBranchMenuItemView
    The IBranchMenuItemView interface provides methods to display branch menu items.
    IBranchUserView
    The IBranchUserView interface provides methods to display branch user details.
    ICustomerService
    This interface provides the methods related to customer actions in a Fastfood Ordering and Management System.
    IFileDataService
    The FileDataService interface provides methods for importing and exporting data from/to files.
    IManagerService
    This interface defines the operations by the manager service in the FOMS system.
    IOrderView
    The IOrderView interface provides methods to view order details.
    IPaymentMethodView
    The IPaymentMethodView interface provides methods to display payment methods.
    IStaffService
    The IStaffService interface provides methods for managing staff-related operations.
    IStaffUpdateChecker
    The IStaffUpdateChecker interface provides a method for checking staff addition, removal and movements.
    IStaffView
    The IStaffView interface provides methods to display staff details.
    IWelcomeService
    The IWelcomeService interface provides methods for refreshing and retrieving branch information.
